message.entry: Input image does not have the correct number of dimensions. Input image must have three dimensions but instead has {0} dimensions.
Invalid scale or size input argument.
Function IMRESIZE3 expected an even number of parameter/value arguments.
SCALE must be a scalar or a three-element vector of positive values.
OUTPUTSIZE must be a three-element vector of positive values.
Specified output size cannot contain a zero.
Specified output size cannot contain three NaNs.
Output size with exactly one NaN is forbidden. Either all three elements of output size can be numeric, or exactly one element can be numeric while the other two elements are NaN.
